{"tid":2141230,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧炳強-強強有冇用過佢枝手炮做愛？","createTime":"2020-08-05T13:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T13:46:56.000Z","uid":8307,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a3047dcc63409af105e9191b4002ecf5b6d2253e","tid":2141230,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T13:34:06.000Z","msg":"鄧蛇-強強 當差當左幾十年<br />\n同江胡人士有密切接觸<br />\n後生個陣又做過下茄呢啡<br />\n佢份人應該好鍾意嘗試新挑戰<br />\n以牙強平時一貫既作風，相信係一個態度十分強硬既人<br />\n係床上都一定好需要比到征服感自己...<br />\n佢玩到呢個年紀個陣條野都已經唔太掂，更加需要有啲新刺激<br />\n唔知佢有冇用過佢枝手炮黎做愛，拎枝炮指住條女個頭逼佢奶槍管令自己起機..."},{"pid":"993c5ca08d5cb7d4af0611e354ec6da819975fca","tid":2141230,"uid":94167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T13:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f090b83e4f8c06675c0711d5d6cb7fcc5a9f3c","tid":2141230,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"打手槍"},{"pid":"fb1240d0c6d3dd13d27324f00009ac6c7cfc67c4","tid":2141230,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0f090b83e4f8c06675c0711d5d6cb7fcc5a9f3c","tid":2141230,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"打手槍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T13:36:56.000Z","msg":"強強有冇打過手槍"},{"pid":"2108ea13fa0d4bb17372e30d410e7c589fdcac5e","tid":2141230,"uid":320902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T13:39:15.000Z","msg":"好似中咗武肺，好耐未出現"},{"pid":"5f1107cdbda84835c54db86090c10e26601a938f","tid":2141230,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb1240d0c6d3dd13d27324f00009ac6c7cfc67c4","tid":2141230,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0f090b83e4f8c06675c0711d5d6cb7fcc5a9f3c","tid":2141230,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"打手槍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T13:36:56.000Z","msg":"強強有冇打過手槍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim